/**
 * NiceClock Design System
 *
 * Three emotional phases, one visual thread.
 * Amber is the constant through wake, briefing, and escalation.
 *
 * Base unit: 8px
 * Horizontal screen padding: 28px
 * Safe area respected everywhere
 */

